Trivia
While the Sunfish was used by Zolarketh and other moderators, it is not a Developer-exclusive ship because it is planned to be available for normal players.
The Spectator-X is the only hybrid ship to not only retain the title of X, but also the only to not be hybrid class.
The Spectator is the only ship in the game without a gun.
The Spectator-X is the only officer class object in the game.

sections.title: Trivia
sections.content:
While the Sunfish was used by Zolarketh and other moderators, it is not a Developer-exclusive ship because it is planned to be available for normal players.
The Spectator-X is the only hybrid ship to not only retain the title of X, but also the only to not be hybrid class.
The Spectator is the only ship in the game without a gun.
The Spectator-X is the only officer class object in the game.
